{"body": "It seems to me that Thor overwriting `attr_reader` (https://github.com/wycats/thor/blob/master/lib/thor/base.rb#L122) is the problem.\r\nVisibility is ignored in this way; i.e. any attribute defined using `attr_reader` shows up as public_instance_method.\r\nThe reason no task is created is of course because of the `no_tasks`-wrapper.\r\n\r\nAny method added using `alias` is less fortunate and becomes a public method *and* a task....", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/13963582", "created_at": "2013-02-22T18:51:13Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/9083#issuecomment-13963582", "updated_at": "2013-02-22T18:51:13Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 9083, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/eval", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/07bd4274c42017bf1ec98de4fb7a0ea8?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F3f9bcd115237155247c4821748e72e68.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval/received_events", "gravatar_id": "07bd4274c42017bf1ec98de4fb7a0ea8", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "eval", "type": "User", "id": 290596, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eval/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237ed20bd3543c151009da1"}, "id": 13963582, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/9083"}
